rrano 2008 (kr. 389,80) \u2013 88 poeng", "Tenuta San Guido Guidalberto (kr. 375,00) \u2013 88 poeng", "To greske hvitviner fra Argyros p\u00e5 Santorino er ogs\u00e5 med i dette spesialslippet, Estate Aidani 2015 (kr. 259,00) og Estate Assyrttiko 2015 (kr. 259,00)."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "kultur|vin"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "ebf8c6d5994e4a4c5d5dbfbf82d7a76d78502475ef9a4825c9e57835fc7effb2"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-08-31T21:07:52.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Dagen f\u00f8r Vinmonopolets store septemberslipp er det Piemonte-fokus i spesialutvalgsbutikkene. P\u00e5 Valentinlyst i Trondheim legges det ut 90 forskjellige Piemonte-nyheter torsdag morgen. Noen av dem er det bare to flasker tilgjengelig av."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article13265690.ece/w5qyb5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Nervi1.JPG"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/219d0f431f216ef535e251887a0df776db90ec72.jpg?5982ffaa"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Piemonte-kupp p\u00e5 Valentinlyst -adressa.no", "Kun to og fem flasker", "Kvoterer ikke", "Fikk teste 14 viner", "Ogs\u00e5 gresk hvitt"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "219d0f431f216ef535e251887a0df776db90ec72"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["vinpuls", "vinklubb", "ulf dalheim", "vin", "database"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "vinpuls,vinklubb,ulf dalheim,vin,database"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["kultur", "vin"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "food-and-drink"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["flasker tilgjengelig", "poeng", "vin", "t\u00f8rket frukt"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["nervi gattinari molsino 2011", "nebbiolo", "rubbia terrano 2008", "san guido guidalberto", "barolo cicale", "estate aidani 2015", "barale barolo bussia riserva 2010", "superiore 2008", "vinmonopolets", "estate assyrttiko 2015", "santorino", "alto piemonte", "gattinara vigne valferana 2011", "barolo og barbaresco", "barbera", "valentinlyst", "laboro disobedient 2011", "argyros", "gattinara molsino 2011", "barale barolo castellero 2011", "nervi gattinara valferana 2011"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["parker", "trondheim", "gattinara"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["gaute skjold", "bruno giacosa barbaresco santo stefano"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["kultur/vin", "kultur"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article13265690.ece/w5qyb5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Nervi1.JPG"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "Piemonte-kupp p\u00e5 Valentinlyst"}, {"field": "og-type", "value": "article"}, {"field": "og-url", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/kultur/vin/2016/08/31/Piemonte-kupp-p%C3%A5-Valentinlyst-13265634.ece"}, {"field": "pageclass", "value": ["article"]}, {"field": "publishtime", "value": "2016-08-31T21:51:25.000Z"}, {"field": "recs-articleid", "value": "13265634"}, {"field": "recs-category-type", "value": "taxonomy"}, {"field": "recs-category0", "value": "taxonomy|kultur"}, {"field": "recs-category1", "value": "taxonomy|kultur|vin"}, {"field": "recs-publishtime", "value": "2016-08-31T21:51:25.000Z"}, {"field": "recs-rawtitle", "value": "Piemonte-kupp p\u00e5 Valentinlyst -adressa.no"}, {"field": "recs-recommendable", "value": "true"}, {"field": "recs-recommending", "value": "true"}, {"field": "siteid", "value": "9222270286501375973"}, {"field": "taxonomy", "value": ["kultur/vin", "kultur"]}, {"field": "teaser", "value": "Dagen f\u00f8r Vinmonopolets store septemberslipp er det Piemonte-fokus i spesialutvalgsbutikkene. P\u00e5 Valentinlyst i Trondheim legges det ut 90 forskjellige Piemonte-nyheter torsdag 